@startuml
title Manage Assignments Sequence Diagram
autonumber

actor "Teacher" as Teacher
participant "Web Client" as UI
participant "Server Action" as Action
participant "Prisma ORM" as Prisma
database "Database" as DB

Teacher -> UI: Create Assignment
activate UI
UI -> Action: createAssignment(data)
activate Action
Action -> Prisma: create({ data })
activate Prisma
Prisma -> DB: INSERT INTO Assignment...
activate DB
DB --> Prisma: Assignment
deactivate DB
Prisma --> Action: Assignment
deactivate Prisma
Action --> UI: Success
UI --> Teacher: Assignment Created
deactivate Action
deactivate UI

@enduml
